Pre-requisite:
1) Need Java 17 and Maven setup
2) Need a IDE - eclipse or Intellij

Project Setup:
1) If using Intellij, go to pom.xml and open it with Intellij
2) Right click on project - SeleniumSauce, open module settings and ensure appropriate SDK (here Java 17) is selected in Project module. In module settings, Java 17 language is selected.
3) Go to Intellij IDEA and select Settings option
4) Select Build, Execution, Deployment -> Build Tools option.
5) Select Maven and ensure correct path is given for settings.xml

Run:
1) Run mvn clean install command
2) Once project dependencies are installed, run mvn test.